===学力===
根据《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》所提供的资料，福坦莫法学院是一所[[美国法学院排名|第一等法学院]]，在2021年法学院排名（2020年发布）中位列全国第27名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/law-rankings|publisher=US News GRAD SCHOOLS|accessdate=2019-05-03|title=存档副本|archive-date=2017-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320195829/https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/law-rankings|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的走读部在全国排在第2名，在[[纽约州|纽约州]]是第1名。<ref>[http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/part-time-law-rankings] {{Wayback|url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/part-time-law-rankings |date=20121214031525 }}, Best Part Time Law Programs [[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]</ref>另外，福坦莫法学院在以下三个方向上也能名列前茅：争端解决（第10）、实习训练（第12）、知识产权（第18）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://law.fordham.edu/ihtml/news-2details.ihtml?id=612&nid=1041 |title=Fordham Law School News Release |accessdate=2011-11-30 |archive-date=2012-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229184613/http://law.fordham.edu/ihtml/news-2details.ihtml?id=612&nid=1041 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>该校[[法律博士|法律博士]]项目在2012年招生时收到的入学申请居全美前十。<ref name="10 Law Schools That Receive the Most Applications">{{cite web | url=http://www.usnews.com/education/best-graduate-schools/the-short-list-grad-school/articles/2012/08/21/10-law-schools-that-received-the-most-applications-in-2011 | title=10 Law Schools That Receive the Most Applications | accessdate=2012-11-03 | archive-date=2012-10-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031102507/http://www.usnews.com/education/best-graduate-schools/the-short-list-grad-school/articles/2012/08/21/10-law-schools-that-received-the-most-applications-in-2011 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志按照毕业生平均起薪将该院评为全美第十八名。<ref name="The 25 Law Schools Whose Grads Earn The Most">{{cite web | url=http://www.forbes.com/pictures/efkk45egmid/18-fordham-university-school-of-law/ | title=The 25 Law Schools Whose Grads Earn The Most | accessdate=2013-03-17 | archive-date=2021-02-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206221312/https://www.forbes.com/pictures/efkk45egmid/18-fordham-university-school-of-law/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

根据[[QS世界大学排名|QS世界大学排名]]，福坦莫法学院被排为世界前50到100的法学院。<ref name="QS WORLD UNIVERSITY RANKINGS BY SUBJECT 2013 - LAW">{{cite web | url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2013/law-and-legal-studies | title=QS WORLD UNIVERSITY RANKINGS BY SUBJECT 2013 - LAW | accessdate=2013-05-28 | archive-date=2020-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124040603/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2013/law-and-legal-studies | dead-url=no }}</ref>

