===就业===
福坦莫法学院在纽约市大型律师事务所中拥有强大的校友力量。福坦莫法学院的校友人数在美国前五、前25和前50的律师事务所中均列第六位。<ref name="Career Placement">{{cite web | url=http://law.fordham.edu/about-fordham/5247.htm | title=Career Placement | accessdate=2011-12-01 | archive-date=2011-12-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111209222617/http://law.fordham.edu/about-fordham/5247.htm | dead-url=yes }}</ref>该学院毕业生在大型律所中就职的优异表现主要得益于其地理位置的优势。<ref name="The Top 15 Schools From Which the Most Prestigious Law Firms Hire New Lawyers, 2008">{{cite web | url=http://www.leiterrankings.com/jobs/2008job_biglaw.shtml | title=The Top 15 Schools From Which the Most "Prestigious" Law Firms Hire New Lawyers, 2008 | accessdate=2013-02-14 | archive-date=2013-08-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130802041624/http://www.leiterrankings.com/jobs/2008job_biglaw.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

根据2006年的美国100大律所的数据，福坦莫法学院的学生在全美50名的律所中找到工作的数目是全国第9，前25名的律所里是第8，前十的律所里是第9。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://law.fordham.edu/facts/wom-fact7.ihtml |title=top ten firms |accessdate=2011-11-30 |archive-date=2012-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217113058/http://law.fordham.edu/facts/wom-fact7.ihtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>-{Law school graduates at top firms identified through “Martindale Hubbell Listings, All” database of LexisNexis, identifying every attorney from any of top firms who graduated from a particular law school.}-</ref>

根据 law.com 的调查，福坦莫大学法学院毕业的学生在全国前 250 名的律所里工作占全体学生的比例位列全国第16<ref name="employment trends for law school grads">{{cite web | url=http://www.law.com/pdf/nlj/20080414employment_trends.pdf | title=employment trends for law school grads | accessdate=2011-11-30 | archive-date=2013-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184224/http://www.law.com/pdf/nlj/20080414employment_trends.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>，大纽约地区第10。<ref name="Employment Outcomes, New York / Metro NYC Law Schools" />在私企就业的学生比例占全体学生的80%，该比例位列全美第一。<ref name="Employment Outcomes, New York / Metro NYC Law Schools">{{cite web | url=http://www.law.com/img/nlj/charts/composite.pdf | title=Employment Outcomes, New York / Metro NYC Law Schools | accessdate=2011-11-30 | archive-date=2013-02-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130204195738/http://www.law.com/img/nlj/charts/composite.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>

根据 2011 年 11 月的《{{link-en|全国法学家|National Jurist}}》报道，从福坦莫大学法学院毕业的在大纽约地区的[[律师事务所|律所]][[合伙人|合伙人]]数量位列第4，在全国位列第13，共有 306 名。<ref name="nationaljurist">{{cite journal | url=http://www.nationaljurist.com/content/where-big-firm-partners-went-law-school | title=Where big firm partner went to school | author=Jack Crittenden | volume=21 | issue=3 | pages=16 | date=2011年11月 | access-date=2011-11-30 | archive-date=2016-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422124437/http://www.nationaljurist.com/content/where-big-firm-partners-went-law-school | dead-url=no }}</ref>

